shibboleth.data

  • Packages that use shibboleth.data 
    Package Description
    shibboleth
    Controllers for the Shibboleth Application.
    shibboleth.actions
    Contains all high level commands of the application.
    shibboleth.data
    The data package contains all classes to retrieve data, such as data from the Github API and stored data in a database.
    shibboleth.data.github
    Functionality for querying the Github REST service.
    shibboleth.data.sql
    Functionality for querying database.
